OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy
OL,6,Fthrough the evening and overnight for
OL,7,FOrkney with some patchy light rain,
OL,8,Fbecoming drier overnight. Mostly dry
OL,9,Ffor Shetland and largely cloudy,
OL,10,Fthough with some breaks at times.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FIt will be mainly dry and
OL,13,Fcloudy during the day but with some
OL,14,Fsunny intervals breaking through at
OL,15,Ftimes. Some patchy drizzle possible in
OL,16,Fthe evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
