OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fand breezy on Tuesday with some patchy
OL,7,Fdrizzle. Wednesday mainly dry and
OL,8,Fcloudy but with some sunny intervals,
OL,9,Fmost likely for Shetland. Cloudy and
OL,10,Fwindy with light rain Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
